    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The exterior shows minor signs of use, such as small scratches, but is generally well-maintained. The interior is clean and intact. All mechanical systems are functioning reliably.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and represents a rare find for a discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no chips, scratches, or dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery still firm and smelling fresh, and every electronic component functioning exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This car has been climate-control stored and meticulously detailed, showing no signs of wear even in the typical high-traffic areas like the driver's seat bolsters or steering wheel. It comes with a complete service history and is mechanically perfect, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this showroom-quality masterpiece. Meticulously maintained and presented in pristine, original condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched luxury interior, every detail reflects a history of uncompromising care. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is a total gem. This beauty has been tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family\u2014it\u2019s basically in showroom condition. The paint shines like glass and the interior still has that fresh feel. There might be a tiny, barely-there mark if you look with a magnifying glass, but to anyone else, it\u2019s flawless. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is a surgically maintained example of precision engineering. Featuring a recalibrated ECU with optimized fuel maps and a reinforced subframe for enhanced torsional rigidity. The powerplant has undergone a comprehensive top-end refresh, including titanium valve springs and a high-flow intake plenum. No parasitic draw, zero vacuum leaks, and the compression ratios are factory-spec across all cylinders. The chassis is dialed in with adjustable coilovers and poly-bushings, ensuring a connected feel that modern steer-by-wire systems simply cannot replicate. Garaged in a climate-controlled facility and serviced exclusively with Group IV synthetics. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanical masterpiece ready for the apex.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Showroom quality. Zero flaws. Mechanically perfect. This is the cleanest example you will find. Priced to move today. Don't wait.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine sliding into a cabin that smells of aged cedar and hand-stitched Connolly leather, where every dial whispers of a more elegant era. This isn't just a vehicle; it's a preserved masterpiece, a time capsule that captures the golden age of the open road. With a silhouette that turns heads like a vintage Hollywood starlet and an engine note as smooth as a cello solo, this car has been curated, not just owned. It glides with a silent confidence that only a machine of this caliber can possess. To drive it is to step out of the mundane and into a story of refined luxury and timeless grace.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly impeccable, showroom condition. This motorcar has been curated with fastidious attention to detail, appearing and performing as though it just rolled off the assembly line. With its flawless finish and pristine interior, it represents the absolute pinnacle of its class. For the buyer who accepts only the finest, this collector-grade example offers unrivaled quality and long-term value.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved like a member of the family, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014always kept in the garage and only ever hand-washed on sunny weekends. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape, honestly looking and smelling just like it did when it first left the showroom floor. It drives like a dream, smooth as silk. I\u2019m really going to miss this one, but I know it\u2019ll make the next owner just as happy as it made me. Come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 45500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously sorted for the discerning driver. This S54 powerplant has been fully bulletproofed with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan components and WPC-treated rod bearings for ultimate peace of mind. The subframe has been proactively reinforced with structural plates, ensuring the chassis remains stiff under high-lateral loads. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox with a lightweight flywheel and an upgraded clutch for lightning-fast rev-matching. Suspension geometry is optimized via Bilstein PSS10 coilovers, providing a perfect balance between track-ready damping and street compliance. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanically perfected specimen with zero deferred maintenance and a linear power band that screams to its 8,000 RPM redline. If you know these cars, you know this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_8",
